messages.content:
I've thoroughly reviewed both files. Now I have the **PerfAI brand identity** clear:

- **Name:** Perff AI (not PerfAI or Perfai)
- **Primary Green:** `#63c29d`
- **Primary Dark:** `#0b1519`
- **Font Family:** IBM Plex Sans (SemiBold, Medium, Light) + Cascadia Code (for code/tech elements)
- **Logo:** The SVG you shared with the distinctive "AI" lettermark

Let me now build the **complete 15-slide investor pitch deck as an interactive HTML presentation** with all the power-ups we discussed.

This will be a substantial piece of work. Here's the full production-ready deck:

```html name=Perff_AI_Investor_Pitch_Deck.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Perff AI — Series A Investor Presentation</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  :root {
    --green: #63c29d;
    --green-light: #8cd4b8;
    --green-dark: #4a9e7d;
    --green-glow: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.15);
    --green-glow2: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.08);
    --dark: #0b1519;
    --dark2: #0f1d22;
    --dark3: #142a32;
    --dark4: #1a3540;
    --text: #c8d6dc;
    --text-light: #e4ecf0;
    --text-dim: #6b8a97;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --red: #e74c5e;
    --yellow: #f0c75e;
    --blue: #5b9bd5;
    --slide-width: 100vw;
    --slide-height: 100vh;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
    overflow-y: scroll;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 300;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ===== SLIDE SYSTEM ===== */
  .slide {
    width: 100vw;
    min-height: 100vh;
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 100px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .slide::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 10% 20%, var(--green-glow2) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 90% 80%, rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* Slide number */
  .slide-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: 40px;
    right: 60px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  /* Logo watermark */
  .slide-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 38px;
    left: 60px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .slide-logo svg { height: 24px; width: auto; }

  /* ===== TYPOGRAPHY ===== */
  .super-title {
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-light);
    max-width: 800px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .accent { color: var(--green); font-weight: 500; }
  .bold { font-weight: 600; color: var(--white); }
  .dim { color: var(--text-dim); }

  /* ===== METRIC CARDS ===== */
  .metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .metric-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark2), var(--dark3));
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.12);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .metric-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.35);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }
  .metric-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--green), transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }
  .metric-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .metric-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .metric-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.12);
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }

  /* ===== COMPARISON TABLE ===== */
  .comp-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    margin-top: 30px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .comp-table th {
    background: var(--dark3);
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
  }
  .comp-table th:first-child { border-radius: 12px 0 0 0; }
  .comp-table th:last-child { border-radius: 0 12px 0 0; }

  .comp-table td {
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.08);
    color: var(--text);
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .comp-table tr:hover td {
    background: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.04);
  }
  .comp-table td:last-child {
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .check { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; }
  .cross { color: var(--red); font-weight: 700; font-size: 18px; }
  .partial { color: var(--yellow); font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; }

  /* ===== PAIN CARDS ===== */
  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .pain-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(231, 76, 94, 0.06), var(--dark2));
    border: 1px solid rgba(231, 76, 94, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
  }
  .pain-card .pain-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pain-card .pain-stat {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pain-card .pain-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pain-card .pain-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ===== SOLUTION CARDS ===== */
  .solution-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .sol-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-glow), var(--dark2));
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.15);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px 28px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .sol-card .sol-for {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .sol-card .sol-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .sol-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .sol-card li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding-left: 18px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .sol-card li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ===== TIMELINE ===== */
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: 40px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 36px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green), var(--green-dark), rgba(99,194,157,0.2));
  }

  .tl-phase {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0 20px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tl-phase::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    border: 3px solid var(--dark);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .tl-phase.future::before {
    background: var(--dark3);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .tl-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }
  .tl-title {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .tl-items {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .tl-items li {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.9;
    padding-left: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tl-items li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  /* ===== FLYWHEEL ===== */
  .flywheel-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .flywheel {
    width: 340px;
    height: 340px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: rotateSlow 30s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes rotateSlow { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

  .fw-node {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--white);
    animation: counterRotate 30s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes counterRotate { to { transform: rotate(-360deg); } }

  .fw-node span {
    display: block;
    background: var(--dark3);
    border: 1px solid var(--green);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .fw-node:nth-child(1) { top: -20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .fw-node:nth-child(2) { top: 50%; right: -55px; transform: translateY(-50%); }
  .fw-node:nth-child(3) { bottom: -20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); }
  .fw-node:nth-child(4) { top: 50%; left: -55px; transform: translateY(-50%); }

  .fw-center {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
    animation: counterRotate 30s linear infinite;
  }
  .fw-center-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .flywheel-details {
    flex: 1;
  }

  /* ===== MARKET BARS ===== */
  .market-bars {
    margin-top: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .mbar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .mbar-label {
    width: 160px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-align: right;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .mbar-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 36px;
    background: var(--dark3);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }
  .mbar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-left: 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    transition: width 1s ease;
  }
  .mbar-fill.green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green-dark), var(--green)); }
  .mbar-fill.dim { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--dark4), var(--text-dim)); }

  .mbar-val {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    width: 80px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===== ALLOCATION DONUT ===== */
  .alloc-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .donut-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 260px;
    height: 260px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .donut-center-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .donut-center-label .dcl-val {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
  }
  .donut-center-label .dcl-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .alloc-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    flex: 1;
  }
  .alloc-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .alloc-dot {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .alloc-info { flex: 1; }
  .alloc-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .alloc-amount {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .alloc-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ===== TEAM CARDS ===== */
  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .team-card:hover { border-color: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.25); }

  .team-avatar {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-dark), var(--green));
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .team-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .team-role {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .team-loc {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  /* ===== TWO COLUMN ===== */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  /* ===== QUOTE BOX ===== */
  .quote-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-glow), transparent);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
    padding: 24px 32px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
  }
  .quote-box p {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .quote-box .quote-attr {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: normal;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  /* ===== MILESTONE LIST ===== */
  .milestone-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .milestone-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.06);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .milestone-list .ml-icon {
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* ===== SCENARIO COMPARISON ===== */
  .scenario-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
  .scenario-card {
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .scenario-card.without {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107,138,151,0.08), var(--dark2));
    border: 1px solid rgba(107,138,151,0.15);
  }
  .scenario-card.with {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-glow), var(--dark2));
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.25);
  }
  .scenario-card .sc-badge {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .scenario-card.without .sc-badge { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .scenario-card.with .sc-badge { color: var(--green); }

  .sc-metrics {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .sc-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .sc-row .sc-label { color: var(--text); }
  .sc-row .sc-val { font-weight: 600; }
  .scenario-card.without .sc-val { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .scenario-card.with .sc-val { color: var(--green); }

  /* ===== MAP GRID ===== */
  .map-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }
  .map-card {
    background: var(--dark2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .map-card.active { border-color: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.3); }
  .map-card .map-flag { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .map-card .map-country {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .map-card .map-role {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .map-card .map-detail {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .map-card .map-status {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
  }
  .map-card .map-status.live {
    background: rgba(99, 194, 157, 0.12);
    color: var(--green);
  }
  .map-card .map-status.upcoming {
    background: rgba(240, 199, 94, 0.12);
    color: var(--yellow);
  }
  .map-card .map-status.planned {
    background: rgba(91, 155, 213, 0.12);
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  /* ===== EXIT TABLE ===== */
  .exit-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .exit-table th {
    background: var(--dark3);
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
  }
  .exit-table td {
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99,194,157,0.06);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .exit-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(99,194,157,0.03); }
  .exit-table .highlight { color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ===== CLOSING SLIDE ===== */
  .closing-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .closing-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .closing-stat .cs-val {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .closing-stat .cs-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .contact-item {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text);
  }
